---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pageTitle: Home
pageDescription: "MarketingX — De meest uitmuntende online marketing oplossingen en software voor lokale bedrijven"
permalink: /
---

{# ============================================
   HERO
   ============================================ #}
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero__bg">
    <div class="hero__orb hero__orb--1"></div>
    <div class="hero__orb hero__orb--2"></div>
    <div class="hero__orb hero__orb--3"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero__content">
      <span class="hero__eyebrow">Marketing · Software · Design</span>
      <h1 class="hero__title">Innovatieve concepten.<br>Resultaat dat <span class="highlight">werkt</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero__subtitle">
        Wij bouwen uitmuntende online marketing oplossingen en software
        die lokale bedrijven écht laten groeien. Webdesign, lokale SEO
        en review automation — alles onder één dak.
      </p>
      <div class="hero__actions">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--accent">Start het gesprek</a>
        <a href="#merken" class="btn btn--outline">Onze merken <span class="btn__arrow">&darr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero__scroll">
    <span>Scroll</span>
    <div class="hero__scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ============================================
   MERKEN
   ============================================ #}
<section class="section brands" id="merken">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header section__header--center reveal">
      <span class="section__eyebrow">Onze merken</span>
      <h2>Drie merken, één missie</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle">
        Elk merk is gespecialiseerd in wat het beste doet. Samen vormen ze
        een compleet ecosysteem voor lokale online groei.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid--3 reveal-stagger">
      {% for brand in site.brands %}
      <div class="brand-card reveal" style="--stagger-index: {{ loop.index0 }}; --brand-color: {{ brand.color }}">
        <div class="brand-card__icon">
          {% if brand.icon == "arrow-right" %}
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          {% elif brand.icon == "map-pin" %}
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
          {% elif brand.icon == "message-circle" %}
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/></svg>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h3 class="brand-card__name">{{ brand.name }}</h3>
        <span class="brand-card__tagline">{{ brand.tagline }}</span>
        <p class="brand-card__description">{{ brand.description }}</p>
        <span class="brand-card__link">
          Meer info
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </span>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ============================================
   MISSIE
   ============================================ #}
<section class="section mission">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mission__grid">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="section__eyebrow">Onze missie</span>
        <h2>Lokale bedrijven laten excelleren in het digitale landschap</h2>
        <p>
          Wij geloven dat elk lokaal bedrijf recht heeft op marketing van
          het hoogste niveau. Geen one-size-fits-all templates, maar
          doordachte oplossingen die écht impact maken op je groei.
        </p>
        <p>
          Door onze eigen software te ontwikkelen en data-gedreven te werken,
          leveren wij resultaten die traditionele bureaus simpelweg niet kunnen evenaren.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal" style="--stagger-index: 1">
        <div class="mission__stats">
          <div class="mission__stat">
            <span class="mission__stat-number">3</span>
            <span class="mission__stat-label">Gespecialiseerde merken</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mission__stat">
            <span class="mission__stat-number">100%</span>
            <span class="mission__stat-label">Lokale focus</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mission__stat">
            <span class="mission__stat-number">AI</span>
            <span class="mission__stat-label">Gedreven werkwijze</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ============================================
   CTA
   ============================================ #}
<section class="section cta-band">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="reveal" style="text-align: center;">
      <span class="section__eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-orange);">Klaar om te groeien?</span>
      <h2>Laten we samen bouwen aan jouw lokale succes</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle" style="max-width: 500px; margin: var(--space-md) auto var(--space-xl);">
        Neem vrijblijvend contact op voor een gesprek over de mogelijkheden.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--primary">Start het gesprek</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
